Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.98,0:24:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, I drank your\Ndrugged wine and you molested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.05,0:24:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I was waiting for you\Nwith a bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't it seem strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were drugs in both glasses\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Hirasaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.23,0:24:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:25:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To relieve my hatred and to compensate\Nfor how you messed up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.87,0:25:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will be your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How can you be so cruel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.84,0:25:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just\Nkill me at the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.48,0:25:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never even once forgotten\Nabout you these past ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to find you\Nand kill you with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.35,0:25:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I have lived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.32,0:25:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lived only to claim revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.06,0:25:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all I saw was a pathetic man,\Nsinking fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.10,0:25:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I came up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.23,0:25:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To restore you to what\Nyou were in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.10,0:25:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and to give you a purpose to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.37,0:25:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And only then would I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.98,0:25:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't care about sacrificing the\Nnurses in order to carry this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.38,0:25:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I became a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.48,0:25:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demon hell-bent on revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.45,0:26:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.59,0:26:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.09,0:26:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Narumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.43,0:26:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.16,0:26:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! You've been\Nin a coma for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.44,0:26:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.10,0:26:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's the chief\Nmedical officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.84,0:26:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.04,0:26:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.31,0:26:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She slit her throat with a scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.42,0:26:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.48,0:26:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we have duties to perform.\NWe'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.45,0:27:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you, Miss Nanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.69,0:27:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.46,0:27:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we're finally together.\NJust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.60,0:27:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
